narratives.question_text: Were the resources available to you - library, fabrication labs, classroom, software, desk space, etc. adequate for the fulfillment of the assigned work?  If not, please make suggestions.
comments: Classes v2 was well set up by the instructors and TA and was easy to use, otherwise this question is not applicable.
Library lacks books, as usual. Otherwise, yes.
The projector in the room is ancient. Either the video conferencing/av equipment are inadequate or the DM staff cannot operate things well.
